properties.name: playlistId
properties.description:
link a playlist that will set what content the feed will include
	 if empty, all content will be included in feed

properties.name: name
properties.description: feed name

properties.name: status
properties.description: feed status

properties.name: type
properties.description: feed type

properties.name: landingPage
properties.description:
Base URL for each video, on the partners site
	 This is required by all syndication types.

properties.name: createdAt
properties.description: Creation date as Unix timestamp (In seconds)

properties.name: allowEmbed
properties.description:
allow_embed tells google OR yahoo weather to allow embedding the video on google OR yahoo video results
	 or just to provide a link to the landing page.
	 it is applied on the video-player_loc property in the XML (google)
	 and addes media-player tag (yahoo)

properties.name: playerUiconfId
properties.description: Select a uiconf ID as player skin to include in the kwidget url

properties.name: enforceEntitlement
properties.description: Should enforce entitlement on feed entries

properties.name: privacyContext
properties.description: Set privacy context for search entries that assiged to private and public categories within a category privacy context.

properties.name: updatedAt
properties.description: Update date as Unix timestamp (In seconds)

properties.name: feedDescription
properties.description: feed description
